  "description": "This individual is a compact, broad-shouldered human of middle years, marked by a bronze skinTone and the thick neck typical of long work behind a counter. brown eyes sit deep under heavy lids, giving the face a settled, appraising cast reinforced by a square jaw and a broken-looking nose set slightly off-center. black hair is kept in a close, practical cut, while a trimmed beard frames the mouth and emphasizes a permanent crease at the corners. The hands are notably large and callused, with old nicks across the knuckles that record years of hard service rather than ornament.",
